

Abstraction And Encapsulation:
------------------------------

 why we need ?
 
   1. To hide un-wanted state and behav of Object for other.
   2. For Security.
   3. To preset Object in simple to Other.
   4. Loose coupling b/w Objs.
   
   
   In Java
   -----------
   
     --> using access specifiers
     
               public,private,protected
               
    --> using packages           
               
    --> Using Interfaces           
   
   